description: Politicians behind much of Guernsey's Covid response win most votes in first island-wide election.
title: Guernsey Election 2020: St Pier and Soulsby top poll
title_page: Guernsey Election 2020: St Pier and Soulsby top poll - BBC News
maintext: There was also a fall in the number of women elected, with eight now to sit in the new States, four fewer than the last term.
